-- Moscow Opposition Rally on Hold After Worker Dies, Interfax Says
-- B y   H e n r y   M e y e r
-- 2013-05-06T11:57:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-06/moscow-opposition-rally-on-hold-after-worker-dies-interfax-says.html
Moscow authorities suspended the
construction of a stage for an opposition rally later today
after a worker died during the preparations, RIA Novosti
reported, citing an investigative official, Sergei Stukalov.  The organizers of the event have been told to move the
stage to another location on Bolotnaya square in downtown
Moscow, the state-run news service cited a department head at
